"# service kdc start\n"
"# service kadmind start\n"
msgstr ""
"# service kdc start\n"
"# service kadmind start\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/security/_index.adoc:1329
msgid ""
"While there will not be any kerberized daemons running at this point, it is "
